<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Flash Tattoos | Queen Marie Tattoos</title>

<meta name="description" content="Browse Queen Marie Tattoos Flash Tattoo Collection.">

<link rel="icon" href="../images/logo.png">

<link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles.css">

</head>

<body>

<header>

<div class="logo-container">

<img src="../images/logo.png"
alt="Queen Marie Tattoos Logo"
class="logo">

<h1>Flash Tattoos</h1>

<p>Luxury • Precision • Art</p>

</div>

</header>

<section class="welcome">

<h2>Flash Tattoo Collection</h2>

<p>

Choose from our ready-to-tattoo flash designs.
See something you love? Book your appointment today.

</p>

</section>

<section class="search-bar">

<input
type="text"
id="searchInput"
placeholder="Search Flash Tattoos..."
onkeyup="searchGallery()">

</section>

<section class="flash-grid">

<div class="flash-card">

<img src="../images/flash1.jpg"
alt="Rose Flash Tattoo">

<h3>Rose</h3>

<p>Beautiful black and gray rose design.</p>

</div>

<div class="flash-card">

<img src="../images/flash2.jpg"
alt="Butterfly Flash Tattoo">

<h3>Butterfly</h3>

<p>Elegant butterfly with fine line detail.</p>

</div>

<div class="flash-card">

<img src="../images/flash3.jpg"
alt="Cross Flash Tattoo">

<h3>Cross</h3>

<p>Classic cross with decorative accents.</p>

</div>

<div class="flash-card">

<img src="../images/flash4.jpg"
alt="Lion Flash Tattoo">

<h3>Lion</h3>

<p>Bold lion design representing strength.</p>

</div>

<div class="flash-card">

<img src="../images/flash5.jpg"
alt="Skull Flash Tattoo">

<h3>Skull</h3>

<p>Traditional skull tattoo artwork.</p>

</div>

<div class="flash-card">

<img src="../images/flash6.jpg"
alt="Snake Flash Tattoo">

<h3>Snake</h3>

<p>Detailed snake wrapped around flowers.</p>

</div>

</section>

<section class="main-buttons">

<a href="booking.html" class="main-btn">

📅 Book Appointment

</a>

<a href="https://web.getporter.io/artist/queen-marie"
target="_blank"
class="main-btn">

💳 Pay Deposit

</a>

</section>

<div style="text-align:center;margin:40px;">

<a href="../index.html"
class="back-button">

← Back Home

</a>

</div>

<footer>

<p>

© <span id="year"></span> Queen Marie Tattoos

</p>

<p>

Luxury Custom Tattoos

</p>

</footer>

<script src="../script.js"></script>

</body>

</html>
